&lt;li&gt;3+ years of BI Tool experience: at least one analytics platform such as Omni, Looker, or Tableau. Omni preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years of experience curating semantic data models to enable conversational BI.&lt;/li&gt;
